This tool lists fonts available in a windows16 environment.

Developed for chasing down an issue with wine and Installshield 3.0.

Building the open watcom compiler under linux (amd64):
------------------------------------------------------

Clone the repo, cd into it.
Edit setvars.sh and uncomment:
# export OWNOWGML=1
Then run ./build.sh
Then run ./build.sh rel to create the rel/ directory

Building this test application:
-------------------------------

Edit Makefile to have WATCOM_RELEASE point to the rel path of your
watcom compiler.

Run make.
